TITLE: Fibonacci Calculation in fib-worker.js
DESCRIPTION: This code defines the event handler for the `message` event in the Fibonacci worker. It imports the `fibonacci` function, parses the input value from the message, calculates the Fibonacci number, and posts the result back to the main thread. The worker utilizes asynchronous module loading to import the `fibonacci` function.
