TITLE: Loading Async Chunks with Shared Modules in Webpack
DESCRIPTION: This JavaScript code snippet demonstrates how to load async chunks with shared modules using Webpack. It uses `require` to load modules asynchronously and `require.ensure` to define a split point, creating a new chunk that includes the specified modules and a callback function to execute after the chunk is loaded. This setup helps optimize the loading of shared dependencies across multiple chunks.
SOURCE: https://github.com/webpack/webpack/blob/main/examples/extra-async-chunk/README.md#_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: javascript
