TITLE: Fibonacci Calculation (No Worker) in example.js
DESCRIPTION: This code imports the `fibonacci` function and calculates the Fibonacci number directly in the main thread when the input field changes. It displays the result in the designated output element. The calculation is performed synchronously, potentially blocking the main thread for larger input values.
