TITLE: Handling Messages from Shared Worker
DESCRIPTION: This code defines the `onmessage` handler for the Shared Worker's port. It processes messages received from the worker.  Specifically, when it receives a "history" message, it updates the chat history in the UI and schedules another history update.
SOURCE: https://github.com/webpack/webpack/blob/main/examples/worker/README.md#_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: JavaScript
CODE:
```
chatWorker.port.onmessage = event => {
	const msg = event.data;
	switch (msg.type) {
		case "history":
			history.innerText = msg.history.join("\n");
			scheduleUpdateHistory();
			break;
	}
};
```

