TITLE: Bootstrap Module
DESCRIPTION: This module bootstraps the React application. It imports React, ReactDOM, and the main App component. It creates a 'main' element, renders the App component into it, and appends it to the document body. It also removes the spinner element from the page, indicating that the application has loaded.
